So, does this mean you come here often?

34
00:01:22,933 --> 00:01:25,992
这是搭讪吗? 你在勾引我?
Is that a line? Are you trying to pick up on me?

35
00:01:25,997 --> 00:01:28,215
拜托 想得美
Please. You wish.

36
00:01:28,249 --> 00:01:31,344
你说的对 我确实想
You're right. I do.

37
00:01:34,839 --> 00:01:37,974
我希望你以后不那么说话
Uh... I wish you wouldn't say things like that.

38
00:01:38,009 --> 00:01:39,659
拜托 我只是开个玩笑  
Come on, I'm just messing around.  

39
