I don't recall your doctor giving you permission to swim yet.

45
00:01:57,572 --> 00:01:59,370
我很好
Uh, I'm fine.

46
00:01:59,471 --> 00:02:01,692
上周你刚刚被电击过呢
Well, you suffered a profound electric shock last week.

47
00:02:01,693 --> 00:02:04,423
