And yet I feel like a thousand bucks.

48
00:02:04,424 --> 00:02:06,021
好吧 那不算很多钱 基利安
Yeah. That's not a lot of money, Killian.

49
00:02:06,022 --> 00:02:07,751
- 是啊 对你来说不算 - 你知道吗?
- Well, maybe not to you. - But you know what?

50
00:02:07,752 --> 00:02:10,111
我希望你下午来趟医院 我要给你复查
I'd like you to come by the hospital this afternoon so I can take a look at you.

51
00:02:10,136 --> 00:02:12,489
- 一点 怎么样? - 好的 老爸
- Say... 1:00? - 'Kay, Dad.

52
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:17,881
你们两个和好了?
So, you guys are just cool now?

53
00:02:17,932 --> 00:02:19,477
不 还没有
No, not really.

54
00:02:19,478 --> 00:02:22,631
但是 这么多年我一直很想他
But, like, I've missed him all these years, and if there's a way

55
00:02:22,685 --> 00:02:25,043
即使让我们达到正常关系的一半 
we can even have a halfway normal relationship, 

56
00:02:25,044 --> 00:02:25,987
我也会尝试的
I might as well try.

57
00:02:26,021 --> 00:02:28,852
还能怎么样? 毕竟他是我弟弟啊
What can I say? He's my little brother.

58
00:02:28,853 --> 00:02:31,905
你是我见过的最好的人
You know, you are the best person I've ever met.

59
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:34,158
- 最好的? - 最好的
- The best? - The best.

60
00:02:44,902 --> 00:02:46,920
英格丽德・波尚
Ingrid Beauchamp.

61
00:02:46,955 --> 00:02:48,372
加德纳夫人!
Mrs. Gardiner!

62
00:02:48,406 --> 00:02:49,455
我正好在找你 
Just the woman I wanted to see. 

63
00:02:49,456 --> 00:02:51,105
需要我帮你找什么书吗?
Can I help you with a book?

64
00:02:51,106 --> 00:02:53,243
不用 我给你带了件礼物
No, but I've come bearing gifts for you.

65
00:02:53,244 --> 00:02:56,547
