As you know, renovations at Fair Haven have been ongoing,

66
00:02:56,581 --> 00:02:59,600
我找到了一些以前的宝贝
and we've unearthed quite a few gems from the past.

67
00:02:59,634 --> 00:03:01,468
- 哦... - 有一样特别的东西...
- Oh... - One in particular...

68
00:03:01,519 --> 00:03:04,138
我觉得你会感兴趣
I thought you'd be interested in.

69
00:03:07,525 --> 00:03:10,277
这简直...
Wow. That's...

70
00:03:10,311 --> 00:03:11,643
不可思议吧? 
Uncanny, right? 

71
00:03:11,644 --> 00:03:13,420
我看到的时候简直不敢相信
I could hardly believe it when I saw it.

72
00:03:13,421 --> 00:03:15,599
她和你一模一样 英格丽德
She looks exactly like you, Ingrid.

73
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:19,185
有点吧 我觉得眼睛有点像
A little, I guess, around the eyes.

74
00:03:19,186 --> 00:03:20,804
她可能是你的双胞胎姐妹呢
She could be your twin.

75
00:03:20,805 --> 00:03:23,668
这个女人一定是你的亲戚 你觉得呢?
This woman must have been a relative of yours, don't you think?

76
00:03:23,693 --> 00:03:24,941
绝对的
Definitely. Yes.

77
00:03:24,942 --> 00:03:26,929
我家已经在这住很久了
I know my family has lived in this town

78
00:03:26,930 --> 00:03:29,115
所以这很有可能
for a long time, so that would make sense.

79
00:03:29,166 --> 00:03:31,164
我很好奇她是谁
I wonder who she was.

80
00:03:31,216 --> 00:03:33,083
还有她看起来为什么这么忧虑
And why she looks so troubled.

81
00:03:33,117 --> 00:03:35,252
你觉得她看起来很忧虑?
You think she looks troubled?

82
00:03:35,286 --> 00:03:36,620
是的
I do.

83
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:48,020
东区女巫 第一季第06集

84
