- 好的 记住我教你的 - 好的
- All right, remember what I taught you. - Right.

85
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:54,855
深呼吸... 设定目标...
Deep breath... Set your intention...

86
00:03:54,856 --> 00:03:56,857
