You're at a whole another level with this stuff.

90
00:04:07,081 --> 00:04:08,955
是啊 太不可思议了 
I know. It's incredible. 

91
00:04:08,956 --> 00:04:11,204
就像... 我突然变强了
It's like I'm... Suddenly stronger.

92
00:04:11,205 --> 00:04:13,372
我觉得我对生活更有掌控力了
And I feel more in control of my life.

93
00:04:13,373 --> 00:04:15,786
我告诉基利安要向前看
I told Killian to move on.

94
00:04:15,913 --> 00:04:17,983
我做到了! 而且当时他没穿衣服 
I did! And he was shirtless at the time, 

95
00:04:17,984 --> 00:04:19,537
所以你知道我有多厉害了吧
so you know I meant it.

96
00:04:19,538 --> 00:04:20,770
他为什么没穿衣服?
Why was he shirtless?

97
00:04:20,771 --> 00:04:22,531
我们当时在泳池里 思想别那么龌龊
We were in the pool. Get your mind out of the gutter.

98
00:04:22,532 --> 00:04:23,896
好的 祝你好运
Okay. Good for you.

99
00:04:23,897 --> 00:04:26,488
现在好像没有什么我做不到的了
It's like there's nothing I can't do right now.

100
00:04:26,504 --> 00:04:29,891
你能灭火吗? 因为你刚刚点火了
Can you put out fires? 'Cause I think you started one.

101
00:04:31,193 --> 00:04:32,893
也许我太强了?
Maybe I'm too powerful?

102
00:04:32,894 --> 00:04:36,647
是的 那... 对 你就是那样
Yeah. That... yeah, that's what you are.

103
00:04:40,986 --> 00:04:42,863
我们该怎么办?
What are we gonna do?

104
00:04:42,897 --> 00:04:45,082
我认为我们没什么要做的
Well, I don't think there's anything we can do.

105
00:04:45,116 --> 00:04:46,917
如果她发现那是我呢?
What if she figures out it's me?

106
00:04:46,952 --> 00:04:49,670
英格丽德 我想没人会因为
Ingrid. I don't think anyone's

107
00:04:49,704 --> 00:04:51,872
看了那张百年老照
gonna look at that hundred-year-old photograph

108
00:04:51,906 --> 00:04:54,508
就觉得你是一个巫师
and decide that it means you're a secret witch

109
00:04:54,543 --> 00:04:59,013
会因为一个古老的咒语而不断地重生
under an ancient curse that causes you to be reborn

110
00:04:59,047 --> 00:05:02,716
你也说了 她认为那是个亲戚
You said it yourself. She assumed it's a relative.

111
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,385
怎么了?
What's going on?

112
00:05:04,387 --> 00:05:06,319
佩内洛普找到了一张
Uh, Penelope found an old photograph 

113
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:09,111
英格丽德在费尔黑文的老照片
of Ingrid at Fair Haven.

114
00:05:09,112 --> 00:05:12,092
你是担心她会认出你来吗?
Oh. And you're worried she's gonna figure out it's you?

115
00:05:12,644 --> 00:05:14,612
睡衣不错哦
Cool bathing suit.

116
00:05:14,646 --> 00:05:16,864
我不知道 只是 我知道那是我
I don't know. It's just, I know that it's me,

117
00:05:16,898 --> 00:05:18,866
但是我不知道我其他轮回的任何事
but I don't know anything about my other lives,

118
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:20,234
我有点好奇
and I'm starting to get curious.

119
00:05:20,268 --> 00:05:21,368
- 哦 - 是的
- Oh. - Yeah.

120
00:05:21,403 --> 00:05:23,473
和我在一起的那个小女孩是谁?
Who is that little girl I'm with?

121
00:05:23,715 --> 00:05:25,486
为什么我会在费尔黑文? 
Why was I hanging out at Fair Haven? 

122
00:05:25,487 --> 00:05:27,741
我认识阿奇博尔德・布朗宁吗?
Did I know Archibald Browning?

123
00:05:27,844 --> 00:05:31,176
不怎么认识 这... 没什么...
Not really. It's... not really...

124
00:05:31,203 --> 00:05:33,839
- 值得深究的 - 没错
- Worth getting into that. - No.

125
00:05:35,050 --> 00:05:36,907
我知道肯定不仅如此 
I can tell there's more to this. 

126
00:05:36,908 --> 00:05:39,136
为什么你们不想让我知道?
Why don't you want me to know?

127
00:05:39,170 --> 00:05:43,390
我不想你被你的前世所限
I don't want you to be defined by all your other lives.

128
00:05:43,425 --> 00:05:47,595
我不想你背负着前世的罪过
I don't want you to carry the baggage of all your mistakes.

129
00:05:47,629 --> 00:05:49,296
什么罪过?!
What mistakes?!

130
00:05:52,634 --> 00:05:54,801
好吧 别告诉我
Fine. Don't tell me.

131
00:05:57,641 --> 00:05:59,609
她不会死心的
She's not gonna stop.

132
00:05:59,777 --> 00:06:03,648
你知道她有多固执 我们应该告诉她真相吗?
You know how determined she is. Should we just tell her the truth?

133
00:06:03,649 --> 00:06:07,035
如果我们告诉她 她也许永远不会原谅你
If we tell her, she may never forgive you.

134
00:06:08,533 --> 00:06:10,784
你真想冒那个险吗?
You really want to risk that?

135
00:06:16,258 --> 00:06:18,292
好的 深吸气
All right, big breath in.

136
00:06:18,326 --> 00:06:20,010
呼气
Out.

137
00:06:20,045 --> 00:06:21,595
好了
All right.

138
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:24,529
还不错 不过你还要进行全面的血液检查
Sounds good. But you should have a full blood panel done.

139
00:06:25,133 --> 00:06:27,301
我有点怀念你的说教了
I oddly miss these lectures.

140
00:06:27,335 --> 00:06:29,470
像以前一样
Feels like old times.

141
00:06:29,504 --> 00:06:33,075
想回到以前 还需要很多努力
You got a long way to go before it's like old times again.

142
00:06:33,076 --> 00:06:35,205
但是... 看到你差点没命
But... seeing you almost die 

143
00:06:35,206 --> 00:06:36,843
确实让情况乐观了不少
did put things in perspective.

144
00:06:37,422 --> 00:06:40,314
向我保证你会去检查 好吗?
Just promise me you'll get a checkup, all right?

145
00:06:40,348 --> 00:06:43,200
不如我保证不再被电击吧?
How about if I just promise not to get electrocuted again?

146
00:06:43,234 --> 00:06:44,590
成交吗?
Deal?

147
00:06:46,488 --> 00:06:47,871
加德纳医生?
Dr. Gardiner?

148
00:06:47,906 --> 00:06:50,255
我对你从莫拉・撒切尔嗓子里拿出来的东西
I ran some tests 

149
00:06:50,256 --> 00:06:50,874
做了些测试
on the mass you pulled from Maura Thatcher's throat.

