But get this, it...

152
00:06:56,610 --> 00:06:59,717
天哪 我没有发现还有病人在这 我很抱歉
Oh, God, I didn't realize you had a patient in here. I am so sorry.

153
00:06:59,751 --> 00:07:01,773
不 没关系 我们结束了  
No, no, it's okay. We're finished. 

154
00:07:01,774 --> 00:07:03,796
艾米 这是我的弟弟 基利安
Amy, this is my brother, Killian.

155
00:07:03,838 --> 00:07:05,785
基利安 这是马修斯医生 
Killian, Dr. Matthews, MD, 

156
00:07:05,786 --> 00:07:08,058
博士 医学研究的超级巨星
PhD, medical research superstar.

157
00:07:08,093 --> 00:07:10,894
我们等会再说吧
Um, we can finish this later.

158
00:07:10,929 --> 00:07:12,563
别介意我在这
Oh, hey, don't leave 'cause of me.

159
00:07:12,597 --> 00:07:16,734
我很喜欢这个有机海绵状骨组织的故事
I love a good organic, spongy, osseous tissue story.

160
00:07:16,768 --> 00:07:18,499
谁会不喜欢呢?
Oh. Well, who doesn't?

161
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:21,071
我不知道加德纳医生还有一个弟弟
So, I didn't know Dr. Gardiner had a brother.

162
00:07:21,106 --> 00:07:24,192
是啊 他喜欢低调行事 可我就出现了
Yeah, he likes to keep that quiet. But here I am.

163
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,195
对啊 干得好
Yep, and here you go.

164
00:07:26,229 --> 00:07:27,481
我还有工作要做 
I've got work to do. 

165
00:07:27,482 --> 00:07:29,831
很糟糕 今天你不是我唯一的病人
Shockingly, you're not my only patient today.

166
00:07:30,829 --> 00:07:33,439
